  "steps": [
    {
      "title": "Use vertex form",
      "content": "Vertex form:<br/>$$f(x)=a(x-2)^2+7$$<br/>Use $(3,53)$:<br/>$$53=a(3-2)^2+7$$"
    },
    {
      "title": "Find the quadratic",
      "content": "Solve:<br/>$$53=a+7$$<br/>$$a=46$$<br/>$$f(x)=46(x-2)^2+7$$"
    },
    {
      "title": "Evaluate the difference",
      "content": "Evaluate and subtract:<br/>$$f(-1)=46(-3)^2+7=421$$<br/>$$f(1)=46(-1)^2+7=53$$<br/>$$f(-1)-f(1)=421-53=368$$<br/>The answer is <strong>C</strong>."
    }
  ]
}
